    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In honorem domus divinae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Sestius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> Corumbus sevir <lb n="3"/>Augustalis ex pecunia sua et <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>honorari</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> ex decreto decurionum <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Cornelio Sulla Felice <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Livio Ocella Sulpicio Galba <lb n="7"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite Spuren von der Verdübelung einer Bronzestatue. (B): Nony: Geringfügige Abweichungen. Z. 7: steht rechts der Zeilen 5 und 6.</p>
            </div>
